(609, 1, '2025-03-07 06:39:16', '2025-03-07 03:39:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>KazUTB is a specialized university for training specialists of a new formation for the food, light, petrochemical, mining industries, for the hospitality industry, business and management, information technology, environmental protection. You can find detailed information on the university\'s website and on social networks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>KazUTB has a multi-level system of training specialists:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>College – Bachelor – Master\'s degree.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The high assessment of the quality of the educational and scientific activities of the team is confirmed by the institutional accreditation of the university and the specialized accreditation of all bachelor\'s and master\'s degree programs in independent accreditation agencies.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>ADVANTAGES OF STUDYING AT KazUTB</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>KazUTB is one of the leading universities in the center of education, science and culture - the capital of Kazakhstan, Nursultan.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Specialized orientation of personnel training.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Affordable tuition fees, flexible payment system.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Benefits for tuition fees for applicants in certain categories.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Military department for all educational programs.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Partnership with leading foreign universities. Double degree programs.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Employment after graduation in state and non-state institutions and organizations.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>For nonresident 1st year students, places are provided in a new dormitory in the \"House of Students\", commissioned in 2021.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>WHAT WILL YOU GET IN KazUTB?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fundamental knowledge provided by highly qualified teaching staff.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Training with the use of modern material and technical base.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The opportunity to bring innovative ideas to life on the Fablab platform, access to technologies and equipment of modern digital production for fast and inexpensive production of functional prototypes of new products and testing of the most daring ideas.&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Internship abroad (Great Britain, Germany, Italy, Hungary, Poland, Bulgaria, Latvia, Korea, China, Turkey, Ukraine, Russian Federation, Kyrgyzstan, Tajikistan) in their specialty.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The opportunity for students to participate in scientific conferences and competitions, sports contests, competitions in the sights of the capital.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bright student life: KVN, competitions, concerts, sports sections.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Why Choose Us?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'why-choose-us', '', '', '2025-04-03 08:17:24', '2025-04-03 05:17:24', '', 536, 'http://kaztbu:8080/?page_id=609', 0, 'page', '', 0),
