(726, 1, '2025-03-07 21:41:00', '2025-03-07 18:41:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Graduates of KazUTB JSC are highly qualified specialists with excellent skills in economics, manufacturing and processing industries, standardization and IT technologies to work in the largest public and private enterprises of the country.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Resources for job search in the Republic of Kazakhstan (specify the region when searching):</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>www.enbek.kz&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Head Hunter&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>rabotanur.kz</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>qyzmet.kz</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>trudbox</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>rabota.kz</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>jooble</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>beam.rz</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;How do I get an interview?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A worthy end to the first stage of the long and difficult job search process would be an invitation to an interview.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>How do I get an interview? How to behave? What should I say at the interview? All these questions are of great concern to applicants for a job, and knowing the answers to them is one of the conditions for your employment. Before answering these questions, let\'s first consider what an interview with an employer is.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We\'ll show you how to get through with an example:&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Resume for Kazakhstan: which format to choose, how to compose it correctly</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sample resume for Kazakhstan.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Resume download Kazakhstan\" and \"resume template Kazakhstan\" are what candidates from Kazakhstan most often look for on the Internet when they see an interesting vacancy. But what should a resume look like?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let\'s use the examples of the following sites.:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>http://working-papers.ru/kak-sostavit-rezume.html&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>http://working-papers.ru/shablon-rezume.html</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>ОБРАЗЕЦ РЕЗЮМЕ</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>КАЛИБЕКОВА ЖАДЫРА СЕЙТ</strong><strong>ҚАЗИЕВНА</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>Место для&nbsp;</strong><strong>вашей&nbsp;</strong><strong>фотографии</strong></td><td><strong>Дата рождения:</strong>&nbsp;08.03.1995 г.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Адрес проживания:</strong>&nbsp;г. Астана ул. Куйши Дина 30, кв 183</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Телефон:</strong>&nbsp;8 707 537 81 82</td></tr><tr><td><strong>e-mail:</strong>&nbsp;zhadyra_95_k@mail.ru</td></tr><tr><td>Семейное положение: не замужем</td></tr><tr><td></td><td><strong>&nbsp;</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Цель:</strong></td><td>найти работу по специальности, расширить свои профессиональные качества, быть востребованным специалистом в своей сфере и карьерный рост</td></tr><tr><td><strong>&nbsp;</strong></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Опыт работы:&nbsp;</strong></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>2013 г.</td><td>практика в «Эталонном центре»</td></tr><tr><td>2014 г.</td><td>производственная практика в АО «НаЦЭкс»</td></tr><tr><td>2015 г.</td><td>волонтер «Международная конференция традиционной музыки»</td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Образовани